snippet.title: Ninja Chowdown Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter: http://kck.st/2TNUO38

Ninja Chowdown is an Android/IOS game that follows the story of Donatsu and the Dough-jo Donuttery as they climb to the top of the food chain . . . chain. The top of the chain of food chains that is. The world is ran by cuisine champions. They are the world's most popular food chains by day and the world's most formidable warriors by night. A strong flavor breeds an equally strong fighting spirit.
